{"tid":1608853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對準奶共大商家即係對準共產黨滲透 會唔會係可行新支線？","createTime":"2019-10-01T12:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T13:54:39.000Z","uid":33579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1eff5addfc83c92cf9faa6d60364a9220cdfcff0","tid":1608853,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:13:49.000Z","msg":"鄭立：對準政權是錯誤的；成功就是香港的東西的滲透度被最低化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1607759\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1607759</a><br />\n<br />\n呢篇文講左除左政治上既滲透，其實係民生商家上既滲透都係好撚嚴重，可以話係渣住港人春袋。<br />\n<br />\n國泰同港鐵就係好例子。發夢見到國殤日好多美心鋪比人拆鋪，吉野家都冇一幸免。<br />\n<br />\n當然唔使次次都去到拆鋪，但用唔同方法去抵制佢地，畀一個清晰信息畀佢地聽得罪香港人，奶共產黨鞋底係冇好日子過，要佢地歸邊，而幫港人既商家就要鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n而抵制大企業比起抵制細企業更有效，因為佢地對政府有更多話語權，全港一齊抵制亦天容易。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485315a07838bc64154e82e161456ac68dbc39c4","tid":1608853,"uid":168359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:21:56.000Z","msg":"奶共無一個是無辜<br />\n<br />\n理應全面抵制<br />\n驅逐共黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2309eae22e8eafd82fb5d9524b0e4e82559a0a","tid":1608853,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:22:30.000Z","msg":"拆鋪都係情有可原"},{"pid":"81b290b2aeda93d796892b30d968924d1e987103","tid":1608853,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af2309eae22e8eafd82fb5d9524b0e4e82559a0a","tid":1608853,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:22:30.000Z","msg":"拆鋪都係情有可原"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:23:07.000Z","msg":"利申我係奉公守法好市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f521406e53c14b98d0b4526fb7e9d31d11d2214","tid":1608853,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:26:01.000Z","msg":"地區遊行其中一個敗處就係冇目標，但如果每一次都有固定支線，就係拆鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，會點？<br />\n<br />\n當然，唔使次次都打爆玻璃，新聞播出黎都會有d難睇，但噴字、噴商標、痴連儂牆都不失為好方法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6face7b9a4e43681f1616571320e978ef43e019","tid":1608853,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f636533cdb1e900ffe1c485c2bd84a5852096b3","tid":1608853,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:27:56.000Z","msg":"向共產黨低頭者，人民自會制裁之"},{"pid":"c83aadbd5f913059313c36ae3ca721221e026b86","tid":1608853,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49a746c652c8e5dc48b8d57f0ac7277ca6b7a1c9","tid":1608853,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:48:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72bcaaf30d69f548df3d33201f16e8ab7107c4b5","tid":1608853,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:51:14.000Z","msg":"點少得建制派議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5be56fdf54cd65682345d72233fc7fb9abaa44","tid":1608853,"uid":322775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:53:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac4eb1dc12de50636331813f3f4bc5827a74778d","tid":1608853,"uid":20916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:54:39.000Z","msg":"食肆係大市場，要人罷食之餘要提供埋alternative，等佢地知可以轉食咩"}]}